`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The TouchProvider uses a **call-based API** (not window event listeners like `KeyboardMouseProvider`). React overlay components call `provider.onTouchStart()` directly via refs. This is the key architectural difference — the provider is a pure state machine, not an event listener.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

